657
00:39:41,551 --> 00:39:44,683
It's time for us to stand up, Phil.

658
00:39:46,829 --> 00:39:49,992
Stay with me.
We'll do it together.

659
00:39:49,992 --> 00:39:53,114
- He'll hurt you.
- It's worth the risk.

660
00:39:53,114 --> 00:39:57,082
You can be your own man 
right now, Phil.

661
00:40:02,872 --> 00:40:04,858
Bitch!

